      "role": "user",
      "content": "i just dont know how im supposed to do this. everything feels so quiet and wrong. it's been a week and i still keep waking up expecting them to be there next to me and then it hits all over again. i cant even imagine a single morning without them. it just feels like there's no point to any of it anymore.",
