    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like... instead of getting better, it's just more of this. every day is just a repeat of the same crushing weight. like i'm just waiting for something that's never coming back. it's exhausting. i'm just so tired of existing in this version of the world. it doesn't even feel real anymore, just empty.",
