      "content": "it just feels so permanent. like this isn't just a phase i'm going through, but just... what my life is now. like the person i was is just gone and there's nothing left to go back to. it's just a constant, heavy nothingness. i don't see how anyone survives feeling like this for years. it seems so much easier to just stop fighting it.",
